    "description": "A systematic mesh independence study was conducted using three structured hexahedral meshes (coarse, medium, fine) with cell counts of 1.2M, 4.8M, and 19.2M elements respectively. Richardson extrapolation was applied to the wall shear stress and velocity magnitude fields at five representative cross-sections within the impeller passage. Grid Convergence Index (GCI) values were computed to quantify discretization uncertainty.",
