    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation results demonstrate that the CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within acceptable tolerances across the full CPB operating envelope. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
